002package com.commercetools.api.predicates.query;
003
004import java.time.LocalTime;
005import java.util.function.Function;
006
007public class TimeComparisonPredicateBuilder<T> extends ComparablePredicateBuilderImpl<T, LocalTime>
008        implements ComparisonPredicateBuilder<T, LocalTime>, IsInPredicateBuilder<T, LocalTime> {
009    public TimeComparisonPredicateBuilder(final BinaryQueryPredicate predicate,
010            final Function<QueryPredicate, CombinationQueryPredicate<T>> combinationFn) {
011        super(predicate, combinationFn, PredicateFormatter::format);
012    }
013
014    @Override
015    public CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isNot(final LocalTime value) {
016        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_NOT_EQUAL, value);
017    }
018}
